    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 showcases the pinnacle of BMW\u2019s naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure dual-VANOS system for optimized valve timing. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M Differential Lock. The chassis has been proactively maintained with rear subframe reinforcement and refreshed control arm bushings to ensure precise turn-in and lateral stability. While displaying the honest patina of a well-loved driver's car, the mechanical components are robust, offering the high-revving, analog feedback that defines this generation. Recent service includes a valve adjustment and cooling system overhaul, making it ready for the twisties.",
